name: Datasciencecoursera
tagline: Course work for Coursera Data Scientist's Toolbox Session
body:
### Welcome Fraser's Practical Machine Learning Pages.

You can access the html code and pdf documents in order to assess my project.
However, we can't allow cloning of our R code due to our code of conduct. 

You can clone or get a zip of the report repository using:

$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages

But the links to the report are here if you prefer to view them without downloading.

[Fraser Doswell's PML Course Project](https://github.com/doswellf/datasciencecoursera/gh-pages)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
